   @2000785 = ~These boots were crafted in ages past by the half - elven Abjurer known as Phenuel the Seer by her (few) friends, and Phenuel the Charlatan by her (many) disgruntled customers. A regular feature in Athkatla, Trademeet, and the other merchantile hubs of Amn, she was a common site peddling her wares; a series of potions designed to do anything from curing warts on various parts of the body to causing the imbiber to fall in love.

Unfortunately, while she was pretty decent at marketing, her skills in the potion -  enchanting department left a lot to be desired and as time wore on she found herself having to skip town more and more often to stay away from angry mobs. Deciding some safeguard to be prudent she crafted these boots, which came in very useful at avoiding the rotten fruits and less savoury missiles which came her way all too frequently.

